Package: lua51
Title: Lua Version 5.1.5 State Machine
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Roy", "Ratcliffe", , "royratcliffe@me.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6594-1280"))
Description: Wraps Lua 5.1.5 state machine using Rcpp. Lua state in R
    becomes \code{L <- new(LuaState)} and garbage collection on that state
    becomes \code{L$gc(2)} in R, for example.
